thread.title: BRIEF-Inspire Medical Systems Inc Sees IPO Of 5.0 Mln Shares Of Common Stock

title: BRIEF-Inspire Medical Systems Inc Sees IPO Of 5.0 Mln Shares Of Common Stock
text:
April 23, 2018 / 10:56 AM / Updated 7 minutes ago BRIEF-Inspire Medical Systems Inc Sees IPO Of 5.0 Mln Shares Of Common Stock Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
April 23 (Reuters) - Inspire Medical Systems Inc: 
* INSPIRE MEDICAL SYSTEMS INC SEES IPO OF 5.0 MILLION SHARES OF COMMON STOCK TO BE PRICED BETWEEN $14.00 AND $16.00 PER SHARE - SEC FILING 
* INSPIRE MEDICAL SYSTEMS SAYS INTENDS TO USE ABOUT $45 MILLION OF IPO PROCEEDS TO HIRE ADDITIONAL SALES AND MARKETING PERSONNEL 
* INSPIRE MEDICAL SYSTEMS SAYS INTENDS TO USE ABOUT $8 MILLION OF IPO PROCEEDS TO FUND PRODUCT DEVELOPMENT AND RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT ACTIVITIES Source text: ( bit.ly/2HnOhpB ) Further company coverage:
